<div class="title">First Time with 2c-t-2</div>
<div class="substance">2C-T-2</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Gandolf&Exact=1">Gandolf</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Gandolf. "First Time with 2c-t-2: An Experience with 2C-T-2 (exp5656)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Mar 13, 2001. erowid.org/exp/5656</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

